hooks.prompt:
Before finishing: if any significant architectural or implementation decisions were made in this session, record them using twining_decide. Check if there are unresolved blackboard questions that should be answered. If work should continue in another session, create a handoff. If the blackboard has grown large, consider running twining_archive.

After completing these tasks, you MUST return a JSON response in exactly this format:
{"decision": "approve", "reason": "Twining housekeeping complete"}
